urn to Smale's 17th problem as originally formulated for\ndeterministic algorithms. We exhibit such an algorithm and show that its\naverage complexity is $N^{O(\\log\\log N)}$. This is nearly a solution to Smale's\n17th problem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Sep 2009 08:43:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Oct 2009 15:43:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 6 Nov 2009 01:50:44 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 16 Mar 2010 03:54:16 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 7 Oct 2010 08:28:48 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Tue, 25 Oct 2011 16:23:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-10-26"}
