ement between theory and\nsimulation breaks in the limit of stiff chains. We discuss the possible origin\nof this feature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Sep 2009 09:56:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
